{
  "stem": "18802.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 326.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I have spoken with a Russian woman who, she's [INAUDIBLE] with her housekeeping, and she would invest something and make with you a knitting parlor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you will give instructions and finish the things, and she gives you a guarantee for living.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I met this woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The difficulty was I didn't speak one Hebrew-- what Hebrew and not Russian-- and our common language was French.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we communicated, and she said she will invest 20 Palestinian pounds.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she offers me a guarantee of six pounds a month.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "With six pounds, I could have my rent paid and what I need living expenses.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I insisted even-- that was my European background-- I don't want this little girl playing on the streets like all the girls.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I need someone to take care of her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "What you will call a kinder menschen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we arranged this, and I found an apartment in the best neighborhood of Tel Aviv, opposite today Grand Hotel [INAUDIBLE], the best neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And I practically was a perfectionist, and I wanted only the best.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this had a beautiful terrace, and I thought, here the women will knit.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it worked perfectly well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a big success.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "The problem, how will you explain the woman what to do?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "You are one week here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You don't speak Hebrew, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So I asked this French woman to tell me exactly what I need-- to deduct stitches, to add stitches, the colors and the numbers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And all this, I put down in writing and learned it like a parrot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when these women came for instructions, and I spoke to them and told them in Hebrew, they said, this woman is a miracle.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
